<h3>We currently keep track of the following items in the Migraine Diary:</h3>
<ol class="round">
	<li class="one">
		<h5>Medications</h5>
		The medications you take, whether they are in response to a migraine or a preventative, may or may not be effective in your struggle with migraines.
		By keeping track of what medications you take, the doses, and the success of the medications, you can determine if you should be looking for new medications.
		<!--
